WEBVTT

00:05:53.919 --> 00:06:00.444
known as NDM, has now spread
from India into China, Asia, Africa,

00:06:00.444 --> 00:06:04.809
Europe and Canada, and the United States.

00:06:05.129 --> 00:06:07.688
It would be natural to hope

00:06:07.688 --> 00:06:11.287
that these infections
are extraordinary cases,

00:06:11.287 --> 00:06:13.145
but in fact,

00:06:13.145 --> 00:06:15.606
in the United States and Europe,

00:06:15.606 --> 00:06:18.322
50,000 people a year

00:06:18.322 --> 00:06:22.446
die of infections which no drugs can help.

00:06:22.966 --> 00:06:26.008
A project chartered
by the British government

00:06:26.008 --> 00:06:29.746
known as the Review
on Antimicrobial Resistance

00:06:29.746 --> 00:06:37.118
estimates that the worldwide toll
right now is 700,000 deaths a year.